dc_description_s: This data represents roads for Menominee County, Wisconsin in 2021. [Road segments representing centerlines of all roadways or carriageways in a local government. Typically, this information is compiled from orthoimagery or other aerial photography sources. This representation of the road centerlines support address geocoding and mapping. It also serves as a source for public works and other agencies that are responsible for the active management of the road network.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of data held at UW-Madison.
